<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow" />
  <title>A Long Time Ago…</title>
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      background: #050507;
      color: #FFE81F;
      font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      overflow-x: hidden;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }
    /* Starfield */
    .stars { position: fixed; inset: 0; z-index: 0; }
    .star {
      position: absolute; background: #fff; border-radius: 50%;
      animation: twinkle 3s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    @keyframes twinkle { 0%,100% { opacity: 0.25; } 50% { opacity: 1; } }

    .wrap { position: relative; z-index: 1; max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 3rem 1.5rem 5rem; }

    .intro {
      color: #4bd5ee; text-align: center;
      font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
      animation: fadeIn 2s ease;
    }
    @keyframes fadeIn { from { opacity: 0; } to { opacity: 1; } }

    /* Crawl */
    .crawl-zone { perspective: 350px; overflow: hidden; height: 380px; margin-bottom: 3rem; }
    .crawl {
      transform-origin: 50% 100%;
      transform: rotateX(22deg);
      animation: crawlUp 45s linear infinite;
      text-align: justify;
      font-size: 1.35rem; line-height: 1.9; font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    }
    @keyframes crawlUp {
      0%   { transform: rotateX(22deg) translateY(380px); }
      100% { transform: rotateX(22deg) translateY(-160%); }
    }
    .crawl h1 { text-align: center; font-size: 1.7rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; text-transform: uppercase; }

    .section {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,232,31,0.15);
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
      color: #e8e6df;
      animation: fadeIn 1.5s ease;
    }
    .section h2 { color: #FFE81F; font-size: 1rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.15em; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
    .section p { font-size: 0.92rem; line-height: 1.7; color: rgba(232,230,223,0.85); }
    .section .big { font-size: 1.6rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }

    .d20 {
      display: inline-block; cursor: pointer; user-select: none;
      font-size: 2.2rem; transition: transform 0.4s ease;
    }
    .d20:active { transform: rotate(720deg) scale(1.2); }
    .roll-result { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; color: #4bd5ee; margin-left: 0.75rem; }

    .back {
      display: inline-block; margin-top: 2rem;
      color: rgba(232,230,223,0.4); text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.8rem;
    }
    .back:hover { color: #FFE81F; }
    .secret-note { font-size: 0.7rem; color: rgba(232,230,223,0.25); margin-top: 2.5rem; text-align: center; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="stars" id="stars"></div>

  <div class="wrap">
    <p class="intro">A long time ago, in a coffee shop<br/>not so far away….</p>

    <div class="crawl-zone">
      <div class="crawl">
        <h1>Episode IV<br/>A New Roast</h1>
        <p>
          It is a period of caffeine wars. Rebel baristas, striking from a hidden roastery,
          have won their first victory against the evil Decaf Empire.
          During the battle, rebel spies managed to steal secret plans to the Empire's
          ultimate weapon: the BITTER STAR, an instant-coffee station with enough
          blandness to destroy an entire palate.
          Pursued by the Empire's sinister agents, one barista races home aboard his
          espresso machine, custodian of the stolen beans that can save his people
          and restore flavour to the galaxy….
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>🙏 Thank You for Visiting Us</h2>
      <p>
        Whether you came for the coffee, stayed for the cats, or just took a wrong
        turn on the holonet — we're glad you're here. Con Leche is built on good
        beans, good people, and the kind of regulars who feel like family.
        May your cup always be full and your foam art always on point.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>⚔️ To Our Fearless Leader</h2>
      <p class="big">🧔☕</p>
      <p>
        This one's for the boss. A true gentleman of the galaxy — kind when it
        counts, calm when the morning rush hits warp speed, and carrying a work
        ethic that would put a whole droid army to shame.
      </p>
      <p style="margin-top:0.75rem;">
        He leads a loving family at home and treats the crew here like an
        extension of it. He never asks more of us than he gives himself — and
        somehow he still finds the energy to push every one of us to do our best,
        every single day. The Force is strong with this one. This is the way.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>🎲 Roll for Initiative</h2>
      <p style="margin-bottom:0.75rem;">A wild order rush approaches. Tap the d20:</p>
      <span class="d20" id="d20" title="Roll!">🎲</span>
      <span class="roll-result" id="rollResult"></span>
      <p id="rollFlavour" style="margin-top:0.75rem;font-style:italic;"></p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>⚡ A Wild Cappuccino Appeared!</h2>
      <p>
        It used FOAM ART. It's super effective!<br/>
        You threw a loyalty card… <em>gotcha!</em> CAPPUCCINO was caught!<br/>
        Your CaféDex is now <strong>1 closer to complete</strong>. Gotta sip 'em all.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="section" style="text-align:center;">
      <h2>💛 With Love</h2>
      <p>
        — from the dev team, the baristas, and the whole Con Leche crew.<br/>
        <span style="font-size:0.8rem;opacity:0.6;">We see you, boss. Keep being you.</span>
      </p>
    </div>

    <p class="secret-note">
      You found the hidden corner of our galaxy. 🤫<br/>
      Spread the word — but let the little green one keep his hiding spot.
    </p>

    <a href="/" class="back">← return to the galaxy</a>
  </div>

  <script>
    // He was found — clear the flag so the next home visit rolls fresh
    sessionStorage.removeItem('grogu_clicked');

    // Starfield
    const stars = document.getElementById('stars');
    for (let i = 0; i < 120; i++) {
      const s = document.createElement('span');
      s.className = 'star';
      const size = Math.random() * 2 + 1;
      s.style.width = size + 'px';
      s.style.height = size + 'px';
      s.style.left = Math.random() * 100 + '%';
      s.style.top = Math.random() * 100 + '%';
      s.style.animationDelay = (Math.random() * 3) + 's';
      stars.appendChild(s);
    }

    // d20
    const FLAVOUR = {
      1:  'Critical fail — the milk frother explodes. Roll a new barista.',
      20: 'NATURAL 20! Every latte today comes out with perfect foam art. The tavern cheers.'
    };
    document.getElementById('d20').addEventListener('click', () => {
      const n = Math.floor(Math.random() * 20) + 1;
      document.getElementById('rollResult').textContent = '→ ' + n;
      document.getElementById('rollFlavour').textContent =
        FLAVOUR[n] || (n >= 15 ? 'Success! The rush is handled with style.'
                     : n >= 8  ? 'Partial success. One order of "the usual" from someone you\'ve never seen before.'
                     : 'The espresso machine makes a noise it has never made before.');
    });
  </script>
</body>
</html>
